m/htm/INews/20140620/gb52019a.htm| title=佔中公投網絡供應商總裁分享對抗黑客| publisher=明报| accessdate=2014-06-22| date=2014-06-21| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006181922/http://inews.mingpao.com/htm/INews/20140620/gb52019a.htm| archivedate=2014-10-06| df=}}</ref>。他表示攻擊者不斷使用新的攻擊策略，相當獨特，是該公司所見過最專業的攻擊。該公司無法辨識攻击來源。<ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1539540/cyberattack-occupy-central-poll-was-most-sophisticated-ever-seen | title=Cyberattack on Occupy Central poll is ‘most sophisticated onslaught ever seen’ | publisher=[[南華早報|南華早報]] | date=2014-06-25 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006175425/http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1539540/cyberattack-occupy-central-poll-was-most-sophisticated-ever-seen | archivedate=2014-10-06 | df= | accessdate=2014-10-02 }}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/25/hong-kong-unofficial-pro-democracy-referendum-beijing | title=Hong Kong's unofficial pro-democracy referendum irks Beijing | publisher=[[衛報|衛報]] | date=2014-06-25 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006181631/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/jun/25/hong-kong-unofficial-pro-democracy-referendum-beijing | archivedate=2014-10-06 | df= | accessdate=2014-10-02 }}{{en}}</ref>

《[[壹周刊|壹周刊]]》报导，从6月14日晚上开始，黑客对投票系统位于香港和美国的服务器发动攻击，攻击源头前三位分别来自[[中国科学院|中国科学院]]、[[中国移动|中国移动]]和[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]。对此，中国移动予以否认，并指《壹周刊》报道不实<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.chinanews.com/ga/2014/06-27/6329026.shtml| title=中国移动驳斥香港《壹周刊》所谓“公投黑客”报道| publisher=[[中新社|中新社]]| accessdate=2014-06-30| date=2014-06-27| deadurl=no| archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629235556/http://www.chinanews.com/ga/2014/06-27/6329026.shtml| archivedate=2014-06-29| df=}}</ref>。

